<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; zoom: 1; width: 911.392px; min-height: 80px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 34px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 225); position: relative; height: auto !important;">Disclaimer:</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; zoom: 1; width: 911.392px; min-height: 80px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 34px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 225); position: relative; height: auto !important;">The above opinion(s), including the suggested diagnosis, should serve as a reference only. The referring physicians/pathologist is advised to exercise his/her judgment and discretion to decide whether to incorporate the provided opinion(s) in the diagnosis-making process.</span></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
