<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">PATHOLOGIC DIAGNOSIS:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Port-A device in right internal jugular vein, removal ---</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">comfirmed.</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Gross description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">The specimen consists of Port-A and catheter measuring       </span><span style="line-height: 1.45;"> cm.</span></div><div>[gross examination only]            </div></en-note>      ]]>
