<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">PATHOLOGIC DIAGNOSIS:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Port-A device in _____, removal ---</span></div><div>Confirmed.</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Gross description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">The specimen consists of Port-A and catheter measuring</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">_x_x_ cm in size</span></div><div>[gross examination only]</div></en-note>      ]]>
