      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>***This is an amended report***. 然後是簡短解釋像The amendment is made to revise the final staging as pT3bN1 (originally reported as pT3bN0) after further review of the material. The amendment was communicated to xxx by email/phone on **/**/** at ** : **. 之後就直接只放新的line diagnoses. 個人覺得是比較清楚. 其他待過的醫院也有新舊都保留的, 不過有時候讀的人容易看錯欄位就是了.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
